{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f826a36021","title":"关于党组织的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"badf1b457c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"f826a36021"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"74fefb4edf","type":"paragraph","text":"关于党粗的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"faea33bc8f","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年三月）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"684ab8c518","type":"paragraph","text":"我们总要有一个党，现在这样的状况是一种暂时现象，没有一个党是不行的。各个革命造反派的组织怎么能代替党？革命委员会也不能代替党。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"68f44aa103","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自张春桥同志1967年3月26日在上海整风会上的讲话）对《缸旗》杂志翻查查报告《“打击一大片、保护一小”是育产阶毅反动路","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"49a5eb027f","type":"paragraph","text":"一个粗成部分》一交的批示","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"403ceed6b7","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年三月二十九日）此件很好，可以公开发表，并子广播。还应调查一、二个学校，一、二个机关的情况。请先印发参加碰头会的同志以及其他同志看一看。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"ddf7b7d1d8","type":"paragraph","text":"关于大批制的指示","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"503bfc1f8c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年三月）一、批制要踏实，要调查确实，不然会一风吹。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"7505008b9f","type":"paragraph","text":"二、文章要一、二千字，短一点，写一个问题。一个问题说明了就行了。不能超过三千字，长了没人看，看了也记不清。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"2a7ec90f22","type":"paragraph","text":"三、删服工具论要批制，但也要有无产阶级纪律，服从、团结都是有条件的。四、托拉斯不能都推翻吧？旧名词可以有新内容，主要批制他走资本主义道路。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"592f782be4","type":"paragraph","text":"关于宜宾题的批示","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"05c8a89c91","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"af114bcbc9","type":"paragraph","text":"许多外地学生，几次冲人中南海，一些军事院校冲进国防部，中央和军委并没有指责他们，更没有让他们认罪，悔过，或者写检讨，讲清楚，让他们回去就行了，而各地把冲军事机关一事，却看得太重了。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"},{"id":"466344e42b","type":"paragraph","text":"·298。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021"}],"page":{"id":"038ef9f642","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f826a36021","start":311,"end":311}}}},"__N_SSG":true}